*konversation-1.6 (02 Jun 2015)

  02 Jun 2015; Johannes Huber <johu@gentoo.org> +konversation-1.6.ebuild:
  Version bump.

  22 Feb 2015; Michał Górny <mgorny@gentoo.org> konversation-1.5.1.ebuild:
  Update dependency on QCA plugins to use USE flags on app-crypt/qca:2
  unconditionally, to provide a single sane path for dependency resolution. Bug
  #541066.

  29 Jan 2015; Johannes Huber <johu@gentoo.org> konversation-1.5.1.ebuild:
  Adjust dependencies to handle merged plugins in >=app-crypt/qca-2.1.

  13 Nov 2014; Michael Palimaka <kensington@gentoo.org>
  -konversation-1.5.ebuild:
  Remove old.

  13 Nov 2014; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> konversation-1.5.1.ebuild:
